;trigger1 = (Var(35)+NumHelper(200)+NumHelper(201)+NumHelper(202)) < Var(36)

;Var(35) = Current Points (Ranked Mode)
;Var(36) = Points required for RankUp
;Var(37) = Current Rank (Starts at 0 for '-' rank (unranked)) or equal

;Upon Var(35) becoming greater than or equal to Var(36), enemies stop spawning.

;After all remaining enemies are defeated, a state change occurs where Var(37) (Rank) is increased
;by 1, Var(36) is increased by 5, and Var(35) is reset to 0.

;Afterwards, the player (and teammate, if not KO'd) is fully healed.

;The Ranked HUD elements are controlled through the Ranked mode states instead of a helper state.

;The enemies that appear are based on the player's current Rank, instead of being random.

;If * (Star) rank is reached, another special state is entered that only spawns the toughest
;enemies. For every 5 enemies defeated here, the player gets +1 added to their rank.
;After 10 minutes in this special state, the bonus game ends.

