;200,6 - Hit ground
;200,7 - Food Power-Up pickup
;200,8 - 1-Up Pickup
;200,9 - Points Power-Up pickup
;200,10 - Blocked hit
;200,11 - Whip Swing
;200,12 - Electrified
;200,13 - Whip Hit
;200,14 - Object Hit
;200,15 - Hit by sharp object (Knife/Sword/etc)
;200,16 - Axel Stand Special effect
;200,17 - Max Def.Special
;200,18 - Blaze Stand Special Sound
;200,19 - Skate Stand Special(?)
;200,20 - Jack Knife Spin
;200,21 - Menu Cursor Move
;200,22 - Menu Cusor Select
;200,23 - ???
;200,24 - ???
;200,25 - Jet Sound
;200,26 - Fire Sound
